data.description: Buyer didn't perform!! Location, Location, and Location, this property presents an excellent opportunity for a remarkable renovation. Less than a 5 minute drive to the infamous Rose Bowl,  whether you're into fixer-uppers of flipping, this project is perfect for you. Nested in a fantastic neighborhood, this property boasts a spacious potential for expansion. Looking for a "Cash Buyer" only. This home sits on a generous lot and presents a great opportunity for income property from an ADU and Airbnb. Not only is the property close to the Rose Bowl, it is also centrally located close to freeway access, stores, public transportation, schools, and dining. No blind offers, this house is being Sold "As IS", with no credit or price adjustment for repairs!!
